---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn more about SoftBuyDeals — your source for the best Amazon.in deals.">
  <div class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8">About Us</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Welcome to <strong>SoftBuyDeals</strong> — your curated destination for the best deals and discounts on Amazon.in. We help you discover quality products worth buying, all in one place.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe smart shopping should be effortless. Our mission is to surface the most valuable products across categories — electronics, appliances, beauty, and more — so you don't have to spend hours browsing.
        </p>

        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>
          Every product featured on SoftBuyDeals is hand-picked and reviewed. We check ratings and verify product details to bring you only the best options available on Amazon.in. When you purchase through our affiliate links, we may earn a small commission — at no extra cost to you.
        </p>

        <h2>Why Choose SoftBuyDeals?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Curated Selection</strong> — We choose products that offer real value.</li>
          <li><strong>Best Deals</strong> — We highlight the most valuable products on Amazon.in.</li>
          <li><strong>Trusted Affiliate</strong> — Every purchase is processed securely through Amazon.in.</li>
          <li><strong>Regular Updates</strong> — New deals and products added frequently.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          SoftBuyDeals was created with a simple idea: make deal-hunting easier. What started as a personal project to track Amazon discounts has grown into a platform that helps hundreds of shoppers save money every day.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
